content.description:
This is the third route right of the boulder that splits Catus Rose cliff. (There is a new unknown route between this and

The Needle Lies

).  Listed in the Shelf Road book as 2 bolts with a tree anchor, this route has been retrobolted by parties unknown....  Now has 3 bolts plus ring anchors.  It has super fun climbing up solid rock. The crux for me was moving up to and past the 3rd bolt.
